---
title: Quick Creamy Chicken Spaghetti with Chargrilled Capsicum Sauce & Baby Leaves
description: Light the candles, get out the red and white checked blanket and get ready for oodles of delicious noodles. It’s spaghetti night, this time with chicken in a rich chargrilled capsicum sauce and chilli flakes to light up your tastebuds. Twirl your pasta until your heart’s content.
